{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be futuristic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Eats</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff0000;\n            --secondary-color: #a30000;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --accent-color: #800000;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin: 0;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            height: 70vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504674904247-74977d742d91?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            position: relative;\n            filter: brightness(0.7);\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.8) 100%);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .menu-section, .about-section, .contact-section {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-section h2, .about-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-items {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .about-text h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-text p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            width: 100%;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 40px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        footer::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.7;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            nav a {\n                margin: 0 10px;\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n\n            .hero-content h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero-content p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n\n            section {\n                padding: 40px 0;\n            }\n\n            .menu-items {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n\n            .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n\n            .about-image {\n                margin-top: 30px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Aura Eats</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Experience the Future of Flavor</h2>\n            <p>Innovative cuisine, avant-garde ambiance.</p>\n            <a href=\"#menu\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Menu</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"menu\" class=\"menu-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Culinary Innovations</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-items\">\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Quantum Quasar Burger</h3>\n                    <p>A succulent blend of synthesized proteins, infused with nebula spices, served on a bio-luminescent bun.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Nebula Noodle Bowl</h3>\n                    <p>Interstellar rice noodles in a rich, stardust broth with exotic, genetically-enhanced vegetables.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Galactic Grapes Salad</h3>\n                    <p>A refreshing mix of hydroponic greens and zero-gravity grapes, with a light cosmic vinaigrette.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                    <h3>Chrono-Chili Con Carne</h3>\n                    <p>A slow-cooked, time-bending chili with Martian beans and a hint of temporal spice.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n        <div class=\"container about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h3>Our Vision</h3>\n                <p>Aura Eats was founded on the principle of pushing culinary boundaries into the future. We believe in sustainable, innovative ingredients and a dining experience that transcends the ordinary. Our restaurants are designed to be immersive environments, stimulating all senses.</p>\n                <p>Join us as we explore the next frontier of food.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541577185703-c715792542d2?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80\" alt=\"Futuristic Restaurant Interior\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Connect With Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Transmission</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2142 Aura Eats Corporation. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}